---
/**
 * NexusLayers — diagrama on-brand de la arquitectura de 3 capas de NEXUS.
 * Esquema propio (no captura, no IA): L1 conocimiento · L2 modos que dirijo ·
 * L3 proyectos, atravesados por la trazabilidad. Usa los tokens del sitio.
 */
---
<figure class="layers">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 760 380" role="img" aria-labelledby="nl-title nl-desc" class="layers__svg">
    <title id="nl-title">The NEXUS three-layer architecture</title>
    <desc id="nl-desc">Knowledge feeds projects through operating modes I direct; total traceability runs through all three layers.</desc>

    <!-- connectors -->
    <g class="layers__flow">
      <line x1="380" y1="120" x2="380" y2="150" />
      <path d="M373 143 L380 152 L387 143 Z" />
      <line x1="380" y1="240" x2="380" y2="270" />
      <path d="M373 263 L380 272 L387 263 Z" />
    </g>

    <!-- L1 · Knowledge -->
    <g>
      <rect class="layers__band layers__band--l1" x="60" y="30" width="640" height="90" rx="12" />
      <rect class="layers__pill" x="84" y="60" width="46" height="30" rx="8" />
      <text class="layers__tag" x="107" y="80" text-anchor="middle">L1</text>
      <text class="layers__title" x="152" y="70">Knowledge</text>
      <text class="layers__desc" x="152" y="94">Everything I learn, linked across eight domains — one growing graph.</text>
    </g>

    <!-- L2 · Operating modes -->
    <g>
      <rect class="layers__band layers__band--l2" x="60" y="150" width="640" height="90" rx="12" />
      <rect class="layers__pill" x="84" y="180" width="46" height="30" rx="8" />
      <text class="layers__tag" x="107" y="200" text-anchor="middle">L2</text>
      <text class="layers__title" x="152" y="190">Operating modes</text>
      <text class="layers__desc" x="152" y="214">Prompts and rules I write — tools I direct, never black boxes.</text>
    </g>

    <!-- L3 · Projects -->
    <g>
      <rect class="layers__band layers__band--l3" x="60" y="270" width="640" height="90" rx="12" />
      <rect class="layers__pill" x="84" y="300" width="46" height="30" rx="8" />
      <text class="layers__tag" x="107" y="320" text-anchor="middle">L3</text>
      <text class="layers__title" x="152" y="310">Projects</text>
      <text class="layers__desc" x="152" y="334">Real work, each with its own architecture, living state and decision log.</text>
    </g>

    <!-- traceability spine -->
    <text class="layers__spine" x="30" y="195" text-anchor="middle" transform="rotate(-90 30 195)">TRACEABLE · VERSIONED · REPRODUCIBLE</text>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="mono-label">One system, three layers — knowledge that scales with me instead of collapsing</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .layers {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .layers__svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border: var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: var(--space-md);
  }
  .layers figcaption {
    margin-top: var(--space-2xs);
  }

  .layers__band {
    stroke: var(--line);
    stroke-width: 1;
  }
  .layers__band--l1 { fill: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 7%, var(--paper)); }
  .layers__band--l2 { fill: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 13%, var(--paper)); }
  .layers__band--l3 { fill: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 19%, var(--paper)); }

  .layers__pill {
    fill: var(--paper);
    stroke: var(--accent);
    stroke-width: 1.2;
  }
  .layers__tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    fill: var(--accent);
  }
  .layers__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    fill: var(--ink);
  }
  .layers__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    fill: var(--muted);
  }
  .layers__flow line {
    stroke: var(--accent);
    stroke-width: 2;
  }
  .layers__flow path {
    fill: var(--accent);
  }
  .layers__spine {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    fill: var(--muted);
  }
</style>
